{"tid":2185506,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7歲男孩泳池內排便被索賠1萬5，家長僅願賠2千","createTime":"2020-09-02T10:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T10:24:07.000Z","uid":38539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"879c436be26875139d0321897c961d55854cfb44","tid":2185506,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mG0D92s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmG0D92s.jpg&h=6a2157e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.cn/A644BcxQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.cn%2FA644BcxQ&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXO%2FcXzH0lQqBACTLtzCSRXY%3D&h=bd7c7284\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.cn/A644BcxQ</a><br />\n8月28日，內蒙古呼和浩特。據報導，一名7歲男孩在泳池內大便，上岸後繼續排泄。該健身房經理介紹，發現排泄物後，健身房馬上開始清理，並組織會員離場。目前，孩子家長被索賠1.5萬元，雙方協商中。<br />\n<br />\n上月28日，內蒙古某間健身房的室內泳池，收到會員投訴有排泄物在池中載浮載沉。泳池人員立刻告知泳客離場，並且開始清理泳池。由於工作人員每天晚上都要消毒清潔泳池，員工對於排泄物的出現感到困惑，決定翻看閉路電視。<br />\n<br />\n透過閉路電視，工作人員發現一名男童不尋常，他先是扶著泳池邊，然後又不斷抬腿、摸泳褲，沒多久後便飄出便便。男童上岸後，又跪坐在池邊繼續便便。"},{"pid":"5ac20d26fdbb7b8b3e323962240a589be39c4508","tid":2185506,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"支那日常"},{"pid":"7041d6313858d7ca7d5981e356caf8bfe6752b1d","tid":2185506,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:07:46.000Z","msg":"支那賤畜係咁<br />\n你幾時有見過畜牲守規矩"},{"pid":"46f23b7299dcd6e165f9780a1a3da4bdaa868851","tid":2185506,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"我試過喺泳池嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff9dc4501f65f4166b1e565789b11beacd8e418","tid":2185506,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"竟然肯賠"},{"pid":"f7ec29e757696c74f7284be4083182ea286fe3ae","tid":2185506,"uid":314611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:24:07.000Z","msg":"急都唔上岸係咩心態<br />\n7歲仔唔係同我講呵屎唔識去廁所掛？"}]}